import React from 'react'
import Navigation from "../Navigation"
import Header2 from '../All_pages/Header2'
import Dimond from '../All_pages/Dimond'
import Portfagain from '../All_pages/Portfagain'
import PortfContact from '../All_pages/PortfContact'
import Footer from "../Footer"


const Portfolio = () => {
    return (
        <>
        <Navigation/>
        <Header2/>
        <Dimond/>
        <Portfagain/>
        <PortfContact/>
        <Footer/>


        </>
    )
}

export default Portfolio
